data.description: If you need closing assistance look on further! Welcome home, where comfort and style unite for growing families or first-time homebuyers, with this 3-bedroom, 2-full bathroom retreat on a scenic corner lot. The 2114 sqft of living space includes a bonus room for versatility. Granite countertops grace the open kitchen, complemented by tile floors and plush carpet in bedrooms. A decorative paved driveway leads to the 2-car garage. Dive into the community pool or make this your haven.
